{"tid":2283840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拒絕祝賀拜登勝選 墨西哥總統：不承認非法政府","createTime":"2020-11-13T01:02:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T11:38:20.000Z","uid":184679,"like":93,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1b7beae68dcadc7682bfd3e743ded7ea518e7b0f","tid":2283840,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T01:02:37.000Z","msg":"美國民主黨總統候選人拜登自行宣布勝選，各國領袖紛紛表示祝賀，但與現任總統交好的墨西哥總統羅培茲（Andres Manuel Lopez Obrador）拒絕承認拜登勝選，他表示無法承認任何非法成立的政府。<br />\n<br />\n《路透》報導，羅培茲11日表示，現在祝賀拜登贏得美國總統大選還太早，他不會屈服於任何壓力來進行祝賀，因為墨西哥並非為「殖民地」，墨西哥堅持自己的原則和政策，墨西哥是一個擁有自由、獨立和主國家，不屬於任何外國政府。<br />\n<br />\n羅培茲強調，他說他在美國大選中沒有立場，將會等到川普政府提出的法律戰落幕，「我們無法承認任何非法成立的政府。這不取決於我們，否則這將是干預主義。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3350452\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3350452&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2ByvaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=018c1e2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3350452&h=614a69fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3350452</a>"},{"pid":"0116e6d59f5160313603cae17f30fae33df8f30b","tid":2283840,"uid":224801,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T01:04:51.000Z","msg":"又幾型喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a60e4f7b4ce8eacec67245ade8604e3715b0d49","tid":2283840,"uid":84081,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T01:05:19.000Z","msg":"對墨佬黎講<br />\n唔認都冇野 拜登標榜大愛<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e55e315371c9b3fff6d58bb49d378ae40a9a35cd","tid":2283840,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T01:05:53.000Z","msg":"但與現任總統交好的墨西哥總統羅培茲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/